
Read these instructions before disregarding them.
To install Gray Matter:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Extract:
	 Type: unzip "Gray Matter.zip"
	 Type: cd "Gray Matter"

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Configure:
	 Edit: inc/config.h
	 This should be self-explanatory.  If it isn't, just skip it.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Compile:
	 Type: make clean
	 Type: make

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Run:
	 Type: xboard -fcp bin/gray

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

If something goes wrong, report your issue [1] or email any member of The Gray
Matter Team [2].  We'll reply as quickly as we can.

[1] The issue list is at: http://code.google.com/p/gray-matter/issues/list
[2] Email addresses are provided in: doc/credits

Happy hacking!  :-)
The Gray Matter Team

